Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:19.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I’m wishing you never let go of me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:24.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君に届く日がくること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:25.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I believe it
